description: What is it like to be part of the group that has been called the most diverse generation in U.S. history? We asked members of Generation Z to tell us what makes them different from their friends, and to describe their identity. Here's what they had to say.
title: 900 Voices From Gen Z, America’s Most Diverse Generation
title_page: 900 Voices From Gen Z, America’s Most Diverse Generation - The New York Times
